name: buyPlexus
overview:
buyPlexus Web 2.0 Shopping Network is a portal for users to connect and explore businesses, products and services.

Consumers can search detailed information on local and national businesses, find products and services by category or location, and discover classified, article and coupon listings from a variety of merchants and service providers.

Business listings include company profiles and descriptions, website and blog links, imported blog RSS summaries, consumer reviews, photo galleries, file attachments, Google Map locations, category inclusion and company contact forms. Customizable coupons can be added to business listings for increased consumer value. Product and/or service classified listings include photo galleries, detailed descriptions and contact information for buying and selling purposes. Article listings include content and photo galleries. All listings are ready to be integrated into users’ social media profiles and applications.

buyPlexus was founded in 2008 and operates out of Lynnwood, Washington.
